Class CircleCalculationResultTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • craj.CircleCalculationResultTable

  • public class CircleCalculationResultTable
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the calculation result data and provides methods to get the maximum value, a visualization of the data, and the circle findings regarding the given reference circle values.
    Author:
    Alexander Johr u26865 m18927, Caroline Rühling u26864 m18926

      • getMaxCrossCount

        public int getMaxCrossCount()
        Returns the maximum cross count. The maximum is only calculated the fist time this method is called. If this method is not called, the calculation of the maximum is ignored, for it is time consuming.
        Returns:
        the maximum cross count
